<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA68">
<l>valimikka vāḷeyiṟṟu vāḷavuṇar māḷa</l>
<l>valimikka vāḷvaraimat tāka – valimikka</l>
<l>vāṇākañ cuṟṟi maṟukak kaṭalkaṭaintāṉ</l>
<l>kōṇākaṅ kompocitta kō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that the powerful Asuras with swords [and] bright teeth died</l>
<l>he put the powerful bright snake around the powerful bright mountain</l>
<l>to twirl [it] as a churning rod [and] churned the sea,</l>
<l>the king who broke the tusk of the murderous elephant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
